<section id="terms-page" role="main" aria-labelledby="terms-title" tabindex="0">
  <h2 id="terms-title">Support Security Terms & Conditions</h2>
  <p>
    At Binance, protecting your account and personal information is our top priority. By contacting support, you agree to the following terms:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Never share your password or two-factor authentication (2FA) codes with anyone.</li>
    <li>Binance support agents will only contact you through verified channels.</li>
    <li>All support interactions are securely logged for quality assurance.</li>
    <li>Your data is encrypted and stored securely to protect your privacy.</li>
